{
  "stem": "11000.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's to degrade him, to-- to dehumanize him, and I think that's what-- what we were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "People sometimes asked you question about your thinking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You-- you weren't able.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You weren't in a state to think like normal human beings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You were-- that's it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember when we marched to and back-- back and forth to the factory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The road you had to march on, people, I guess, didn't have a sewer system.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had a gutter, and the garbage was thrown in the gutter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then, when the rain came, it washed away the thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, the trick was, when you had to march-- we always had to line up in five-- to be on the outside so that you're close to the gutter so when you could spot something that was edible that you took a quick [? grab ?] and-- and then have something to eat.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "If you were caught doing this by the guards, you were punished.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Your number was written down, and then, once a week or so, they had payday, what they called.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You had to line up, and the numbers were called.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then you got your punishment for what you did, depending on how many lashes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Usually, when you get over the 30 mark, you didn't get up anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That was the end of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But it didn't mean anything to you because your reactions-- you weren't thinking of what can happen to you if you get caught.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "All was on your mind was there was something to eat, and you had to go for it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that's how you lived, day in and day out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The Germans were always, how should I say, very culturally thinking.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
